# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  StudentSIS Lao — .gitignore
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── DATABASE (PII: student personal data — NEVER commit) ──
sis_lao.db
sis_lao.db-journal
sis_lao.db-wal
sis_lao.db-shm
*.db-backup

# ── .NET build output ──
bin/
obj/
publish/
installer-output/

# ── Visual Studio local files ──
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# ── Rider / VS Code ──
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# ── NuGet ──
packages/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/

# ── Windows ──
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# ── macOS (in case someone clones on Mac) ──
.DS_Store

# ── OS temp / logs ──
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak

# ── Scratchpad (Claude Code temp files if any leak in) ──
scratchpad/

# ── Claude Code local prefs (per-user tool settings) ──
.claude/

# ── Loose test-output files at project root
#    (canonical copies of these templates live in Templates/ — commit
#    those; the root ones are stray exports / work-in-progress and
#    shouldn't ship in the repo). Only matches at repo root, not subdirs.
/report *.xlsx
/templete*.xlsx
/ລາຍງານປະຫວັດນັກຮຽນ.docx
/ລີພອດຄະແນນບຸກຄົນ.xlsx

# ── Explicitly KEEP source assets that .NET gitignore templates
#    sometimes over-eagerly exclude:
!Templates/*.docx
!Templates/*.xlsx
!Assets/*.png
!Assets/*.ico
!installer/*.iss
!installer/*.cmd
!installer/User-Manual.pdf
